        </p>
        <p>
          From project charter, technical specification, and test plan to Microsoft Project schedule and Pivotal Tracker user stories, to development, testing and implementation, our professors made sure we worked through every step of the development process in order to understand what it takes to ensure quality in all aspects of software development.
        </p>
        <p>
